---
import Tooltip from './Tooltip.astro';
---

<link rel="preload" href="/self.png" as="image" />

<aside class="sidebar">
  <img src="/self.png" draggable="false" alt="Profile Photo" class="pfp" />
  <h1>Hershraj Niranjani</h1>
  <span class="contact">hershraj [at] berkeley.edu</span>
  <p class="location">San Francisco, CA</p>

  <div class="bio">
    <p>
      I'm a Member of Technical Staff at a stealth-mode startup, where I'm building the future of AI-native video alongside an incredible team. On the side, I am wrapping up my EECS undergrad degree at UC Berkeley.
    </p>

    <p>
      Before this, I spent time at BAIR working on LLM-guided program synthesisâ€”figuring out how to make language 
      models navigate massive combinatorial search spaces efficiently. That work taught me a lot about what these 
      systems can (and can't) do well.
    </p>

    <p>
      I've also built agentic systems and efficient web-crawling algorithms at Virio, shipped deep learning models for real estate 
      forecasting at Property Finder, and built a startup regarding enterprise AI observability as part of The Residency (Cohort 3). The common problem I have worked on is  
